      {
         "title":"",
         "text":
			"Well done stealing the Aegis prototype. This is how we'll win the war. 
			Our satellites are showing heavy enemy resistance blocking your escape.
			Imperial forces want their weapon back.
			Let's not give it to them.
			(WASD to move, space to shoot)"
      },
      {
      	"title":"",
      	"text":
      		"Great work Taylor. Our airstrikes destroyed what was left of the weapons lab.
			Every assault we make on the capital is thwarted. The Empire's moon based defense
			system is too strong. We need you to destroy it.
			Unfortunately, Aegis is incapable of space flight. You'll have to fight your
			way into the Empire's launch facility and commandeer a shuttle.
			Be careful you're entering enemy controlled territory."
      },
      {
      	"title":"",
      	"text":
			"Well done. You're at the outskirts of the base now.
			Our intel suggests a few patrols, but nothing that you can't handle."
      },
      {
      	"title":"",
      	"text":
			"You're in the base. Our satellites are showing proximity mines.
			Best to not get too close ..."
